@hailstoneTV @tobiassolem Hmm looking more into it, the topic is a lot more complicated than I first assumed. EMP devices basically work by overcharging exposed wires and circuits. @hailstoneTV @tobiassolem EMP detonations do not destroy small voltage electronics like holo sights. It really only poses a threat to power grids(one was already detonated).
